---
title: Garlicky Lamb Rissoles & Extra Cheesy Wedges with Cucumber Salad & Herby Mayo
description: Lamb mince can raise rissoles to number one in our dinner time charts. They are the fan fave when you can dip them in a herby
mayo. The secret to fame for this dish is melting Parmesan cheese over golden wedges.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6719c4ecc2f9d9459122c0ca-8c6bb483.jpeg
